Day 1: Started learning TypeScript

Completed with the introduction and basic environment setup for TypeScript.

TypeScript

>>It is a language for appliction-scale JavaScript development.

>>TypeScript is a typed superset of JS that compiles to plain JS.

Design Goals

>>Adds support for classes, interfaces and modules.
>>Development tooling support


Installation 
npm install -g typescript


This will install TypeScript globally. After installation, 
it will be available via the tsc command.